toolBar.lock: Eǧǧ afecku n tefrayt yermed mbaɛd asuneɣ

hints.canvasPanning: Akken ad tesmuttiḍ taɣzut n usuneɣ, ṭṭef ṛṛuda n umumed, neɣ seqdec afecku Afus
hints.linearElement: Ssit akken ad tebduḍ aṭas n tenqiḍin, zuɣer i yiwen n yizirig
hints.freeDraw: Ssit yerna zuɣer, serreḥ ticki tfukeḍ
hints.text: Tixidest: tzemreḍ daɣen ad ternuḍ aḍris s usiti snat n tikkal anida tebɣiḍ s ufecku n tefrayt
hints.text_selected: Ssit snat n tikkal neɣ ssed taqeffalt Kcem akken ad tẓergeḍ aḍris
hints.text_editing: Ssit Escape neɣ CtrlOrCmd+ENTER akken ad tfakkeḍ asiẓreg
hints.linearElementMulti: Ssit ɣef tenqiḍt taneggarut neɣ ssed taqeffalt Escape neɣ taqeffalt Kcem akken ad tfakkeḍ
hints.lockAngle: Tzemreḍ ad tḥettmeḍ tiɣmert s tuṭṭfa n tqeffalt SHIFT
hints.resize:
Tzemreḍ ad tḥettemeḍ assaɣ s tuṭṭfa n tqeffalt SHIFT mi ara tettbeddileḍ tiddi,
ma teṭṭfeḍ ALT abeddel n tiddi ad yili si tlemmast
hints.resizeImage:
Tzemreḍ ad talseḍ tiddi s tilelli s tuṭṭfa n SHIFT,
ṭṭef ALT akken ad talseḍ tiddi si tlemmast
hints.rotate: Tzemreḍ ad tḥettemeḍ tiɣemmar s tuṭṭfa n SHIFT di tuzzya
hints.lineEditor_info: Ssed ɣef CtrlOrCmd yerna ssit snat n tikkal neɣ ssed ɣef CtrlOrCmd + Kcem akken ad tẓergeḍ tineqqiḍin
hints.lineEditor_pointSelected:
Ssed taqeffalt kkes akken ad tekkseḍ tanqiḍ (tinqiḍin),
CtrlOrCmd+D akken ad tsiselgeḍ, neɣ zuɣer akken ad tesmuttiḍ
hints.lineEditor_nothingSelected:
Fren tanqiḍt akken ad tẓergeḍ (ṭṭef SHIFT akken ad tferneḍ aṭas),
neɣ ṭṭef Alt akken ad ternuḍ tinqiḍin timaynutin
hints.placeImage: Ssit akken ad tserseḍ tugna, neɣ ssit u zuɣer akken ad tesbaduḍ tiddi-ines s ufus
hints.bindTextToElement: Ssed ɣef kcem akken ad ternuḍ aḍris
hints.deepBoxSelect: Ṭṭef CtrlOrCmd akken ad tferneḍ s telqey, yerna ad trewleḍ i uzuɣer
hints.eraserRevert: Ssed Alt akken ad tsefsxeḍ iferdisen yettwacerḍen i tukksa

errorSplash.headingMain: Teḍra-d tuccḍa. Eɛreḍ <button>asali n usebter tikkelt-nniḍen.</button>
errorSplash.clearCanvasMessage: Ma yella tulsa n usali ur tefri ara ugur, eɛreḍ <button>asfaḍ n teɣzut n usuneɣ.</button>
errorSplash.clearCanvasCaveat: Ayagi ad d-iglu s usṛuḥu n umahil
errorSplash.trackedToSentry: Tuccḍa akked umesmagi {{eventId}} tettwasekles deg unagraw-nneɣ.
errorSplash.openIssueMessage: Nḥuder aṭas akken ur nseddu ara talɣut n usayes-inek (m) di tuccḍa. Ma yella asayes-inek (m) mačči d amaẓlay, ttxil-k (m) xemmem ad ḍefreḍ <button>afecku n weḍfar n yibugen.</button> Ma ulac uɣilif seddu talɣut ukessar-agi s wenɣal akked usenṭeḍ di GitHub issue.

roomDialog.desc_intro: Tzemreḍ ad d-teɛerḍeḍ medden ɣer usayes-inek (m) amiran akken ad ttekkin yid-k.
roomDialog.desc_privacy: Ur tqelliq ara, tiɣimit tsseqdac awgelhen ixef s ixef, dɣa ayen ara tsunɣeḍ ad iqqim d amaẓlay. Ula d aqeddac-nneɣ ur yezmir ara ad iwali acu txeddemeḍ.
roomDialog.desc_inProgressIntro: Tiɣimit n umɛawen s srid tetteddu akka tura.
roomDialog.desc_shareLink: Bḍu aseɣwen-agi akked medden ukud tebɣiḍ ad temɛawaneḍ:
roomDialog.desc_exitSession: Aḥbas n tɣimit ad k (m) yesenser si texxamt, maca ad tizmireḍ ad tkemmeleḍ amahil s usayes, s wudem adigan. Ẓer belli ayagi ur yettḥaz ara imdanen-nniḍen, yerna ad izmiren ad kemmelen ad mɛawanen di tsuffeɣt-nnsen.
roomDialog.shareTitle: Rnu ɣer tɣimit n umɛiwen s srid n Excalidraw

exportDialog.disk_details: Sekles isefka n usayes deg ufaylu ansi ara tizmireḍ ad d-tketreḍ areḍqal.

publishDialog.noteDescription: Azen tamkarḍit-inek•inem akken ad teddu di <link>akaram azayez n temkarḍit</link>i yimdanen-nniḍen ara isqedcen deg wunuɣen-nnsen.
publishDialog.noteGuidelines: Tamkarḍit teḥwaǧ ad tettwaqbel s ufus qbel. Ma ulac uɣilif ɣer <link>iwellihen</link> send ad tazneḍ. Tesriḍ amiḍan n GitHub akken ad tmmeslayeḍ yerna ad tgeḍ ibeddilen ma yelaq, maca mačči d ayen yettwaḥetmen.
publishDialog.noteLicense: Mi tuzneḍ ad tqebleḍ akken tamkarḍit ad d-teffeɣ s <link>Turagt MIT, </link>ayen yebɣan ad d-yini belli yal yiwen izmer ad ten-iseqdec war tilist.
publishDialog.noteItems: Yal aferdis n temkarḍit isefk ad isɛu isem-is i yiman-is akken ad yili wamek ara yettusizdeg. Iferdisen-agi n temkarḍit ad ddun:
publishDialog.atleastOneLibItem: Ma ulac uɣilif fern ma drus yiwen n uferdis n temkarḍit akken ad tebduḍ
publishDialog.republishWarning: Tamawt: kra n yiferdisen yettwafernen ttwacerḍen ffeɣen-d/ttwaznen. Isefk ad talseḍ tuzzna n yiferdisen anagar mi ara tleqqemeḍ tamkarḍit neɣ tuzzna yellan.
